{{!-- too big but thats later --}}
<ul class="sg-colors" style="background: #fafafa ">
    {{# items }}
        <li>
            <span class="sg-swatch" style="background: {{ value }}; clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 0 100%);"></span>
            <span class="sg-label">
                {{ name }}
                <br />Hex {{ value }}
                <br />Contrast {{ contrast-white }}
                <br />Normal Text AA {{ white-normal-AA }}
                <br />Normal Text AAA {{ white-normal-AAA }}
                <br />Large Text AA {{ white-large-AA }}
                <br />Large Text AAA {{ white-large-AAA }}
                <br />UI {{ white-UI }}
            </span>
        </li>
    {{/ items }}
</ul>
<small>{{{ meta.description }}}</small>

Perfers Color Scheme black
<ul class="sg-colors">
    {{# items }}
        <li style="background-color: #0a0a0a;">
            <span class="sg-swatch" style="background: {{ value }}; clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 0 100%);"></span>
            {{!-- clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 0 100%); --}}
            <span class="sg-label" style="color: #fefefe;">
                {{!-- style="color: #fefefe;" --}}
                {{ name }}
                <br />Hex {{ value }}
                <br />Contrast {{ contrast-black }}
                <br />Normal Text AA {{ black-normal-AA }}
                <br />Normal Text AAA {{ black-normal-AAA }}
                <br />Large Text AA {{ black-large-AA }}
                <br />Large Text AAA {{ black-large-AAA }}
                <br />UI {{ black-UI }}
            </span>
        </li>
    {{/ items }}
</ul>
<small>{{{ meta.description }}}</small>

{{!-- 
This would be 100x nicer if it was styled or automatic but this is base level

WCAG 2.0 level AA
requires a contrast ratio of at least
4.5:1 for normal text
3:1 for large text.

WCAG 2.1 requires a contrast ratio of at least
3:1 for graphics and user interface components (such as form input borders).

WCAG Level AAA requires a contrast ratio of at least
7:1 for normal text
4.5:1 for large text. 
--}}